<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    <title>Vitation</title>

    <style>
        #vitation {
            width: 140px;
            height: 78px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        #social {
            padding: 12px;
            margin-right: 20px;
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            background-color: #E7EFF5;
            border-radius: 50px;
            display: inline-block;
            vertical-align: middle;
        }

        .main-content {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 70px;
        }

        .desktop {
            display: block;
            padding-top: 50px;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        .mobile {
            display: none;
        }

        #alamat {
            margin-top: 70px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        #footer {
            margin-top: 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        h2 {
            font-family: "Arial";
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 24px;
            line-height: 30px;
            letter-spacing: 0.17%;
            color: #1F335B !important;
            margin: 0 0 32px 0;
        }

        h3 {
            font-family: "Arial";
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 20px;
            line-height: 30px;
            letter-spacing: 0.17%;
            color: #1F335B !important;
            margin: 0;
        }

        p {
            font-family: "Arial";
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 400;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 12px;
            letter-spacing: 0.17%;
            color: #79859D;
            margin: 0 0 12px 0;
        }

        #body3 {
            font-family: "Arial";
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: normal;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 150%;
            margin: 0px;
            color: #79859D !important;
        }

        span {
            font-family: "Arial";
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 30px;
            color: #001242 !important;
        }

        button {
            margin-top: 8px;
            width: 313px;
            height: 44px;
            font-family: "Arial";
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 16px;
            letter-spacing: 0px;
            text-align: center;
            background: linear-gradient(267.32deg, #ffe300 -22.12%, #ffe300 55.77%, #ffe300 127.43%);
            color: #000;
            border-width: 0px;
            cursor: pointer;
            border-radius: 50px;
        }

        a {
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 24px;
        }

        hr {
            border: 1px solid rgba(33, 33, 33, 0.08);
            line-height: 40px;
        }

        #row {
            display: flex;
        }

        #inline-block {
            display: inline-block;
        }

        #table--586 {
            border-radius: 20px;
            width: 790px;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 30px rgba(13, 91, 159, 0.1);
            text-align: "center";
            margin: 16px 0 0 0;
            padding: 40px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border: "0";
        }

        #column__detail {
            float: left;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
            width: 50%;
        }

        #column__button {
            text-align: center;
        }

        #text__body {
            font-family: "Arial";
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 400;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 24px;
            color: #79859D;
            margin-bottom: 0px;
        }

        #text__body--idr {
            font-family: "Arial";
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 24px;
            color: #1F335B;
            margin-bottom: 0px;
        }

        @media (min-width: 1281px) {
            #td--586 {
                padding: 48px 40px 32px 40px;
            }

            #table--790 {
                width: 790px;
            }
        }

        @media (min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 1280px) {
            #td--586 {
                padding: 64px 40px 32px 40px;
            }

            #table--790 {
                width: 790px;
            }

            .main-content {
                margin-top: 30px;
            }

            #alamat {
                margin-top: 40px;
                text-align: center;
            }
        }

        @media (min-width: 768px) and (max-width: 1024px) {
            #td--586 {
                padding: 64px 40px 32px 40px;
            }

            #table--790 {
                width: 640px;
            }

            .main-content {
                margin-top: 30px;
            }

            #alamat {
                margin-top: 40px;
                text-align: center;
            }
        }

        @media (min-width: 768px) and (max-width: 1024px) and (orientation: landscape) {
            #td--586 {
                padding: 64px 40px 32px 40px;
            }

            #table--790 {
                width: 640px;
            }

            .main-content {
                margin-top: 30px;
            }

            #alamat {
                margin-top: 40px;
                text-align: center;
            }
        }

        @media (min-width: 481px) and (max-width: 767px) {
            .mobile {
                display: block;
                padding-top: 50px;
                padding-left: 15px;
            }

            .desktop {
                display: none;
            }

            #td--586 {
                padding: 64px 40px 32px 40px;
            }

            #table--790 {
                width: 600px;
            }

            button {
                width: 100%;
            }

            .main-content {
                margin-top: 30px;
            }

            #alamat {
                margin-top: 40px;
                text-align: center;
            }
        }

        @media (min-width: 320px) and (max-width: 480px) {
            .mobile {
                display: block;
                padding-top: 50px;
                padding-left: 15px;
            }

            .desktop {
                display: none;
            }

            #td--586 {
                padding: 48px 16px 32px 16px;
            }

            #text__body {
                font-size: 11px;
            }

            #text__body--idr {
                font-size: 12px;
            }

            #social {
                width: 24px;
                height: 24px;
                margin-right: 8px;
            }

            a {
                font-size: 8px;
                line-height: 8px;
            }

            #table--790 {
                width: 100%;
            }

            #column {
                width: 100%;
            }

            #table--586 {
                width: 100%;
                padding: 16px;
            }

            p {
                margin-bottom: 8px;
            }

            h2 {
                font-size: 16px;
                margin-bottom: 16px;
            }

            h3 {
                font-size: 14px;
            }

            #body3 {
                font-size: 10px;
            }

            #column__detail {
                margin-bottom: 16px;
            }

            p,
            span {
                font-size: 14px;
            }

            button {
                width: 80%;
                padding: 5px;
            }

            .main-content {
                margin-top: 30px;
            }

            #alamat {
                margin-top: 40px;
                text-align: center;
            }
        }

        @media screen and (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
            p {
                color: #001242;
            }

            #table--586 {
                background-color: #ffffff;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div id="main-container">
        <div style="text-align: center;">
            <img src="https://imgur.com/hdMA8wr.png" width="30%" id="logo" alt="logo-black-png">
        </div>

        <div class="main-content">
            <h2>Hi, {{name}}</h2>
            <p>Congrats, Your account has been created.</p>
            <p>
                Your username is: <span>{{username}}</span>
            </p>
            <p>TO FINISH SIGNING UP AND ACTIVATE YOUR ACCOUNT YOU JUST NEED TO SET YOUR PASSWORD.</p>

            <a href="{{url}}" target="_blank">
                <button>Activate My Account</button>
            </a>
        </div>

        <div id="alamat">
            <h2>PT Vitation Indonesia</h2>
            <p>Jl. Bangka Raya No.10a, RT.2/RW.5, Pela Mampang, Kec. Mampang Prpt., Kota Jakarta Selatan, Daerah Khusus
                Ibukota Jakarta 12720</p>
            <p>Informasi lebih lanjut? Hubungi kami di 081 234 567 890 | <a
                    href="www.vitation.co.id">www.vitation.co.id</a>
        </div>
        </p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>